WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.880 --> 00:00:10.400
All those who come for the first time
to a program of Sahaja Yoga,

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:16.000
because of the dedication
of a few Sahaja Yogis,

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.480
they are called, who live around here,

00:00:18.480 --> 00:00:23.680
Her Holiness Mataji Nirmala Devi
has very graciously accepted

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:29.440
to come here and to talk to us.

00:00:32.080 --> 00:00:41.760
It is not easy to introduce a reality
which is beyond words,

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:52.160
which is deep, genuine,
which is at the core of what we are seeking.

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:59.040
And the difficulty is the greater
in this time, now,

00:00:59.040 --> 00:01:09.600
because the spiritual scene has been invaded
by all sorts of people,

00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:20.560
pseudo-teachers, who offer many things,
many experiences,

00:01:20.560 --> 00:01:25.440
which, instead of taking us
nearer to ourselves,

00:01:25.440 --> 00:01:28.080
take us away from us.

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:37.520
Sahaja Yoga is a very, very simple
and yet tremendous process,

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:42.960
whereby our attention is sucked inside,

00:01:42.960 --> 00:01:47.760
is sucked inside by the raising
of a potential energy

00:01:47.760 --> 00:01:54.240
which is within each of us,
as Mataji is going to explain.

00:01:54.240 --> 00:02:02.080
It is unbelievable, and therefore,
no one asks you to believe.

00:02:02.080 --> 00:02:06.240
It is unbelievable that such
an incredible happening,

00:02:06.240 --> 00:02:10.560
that you can actually
get connected with yourself,

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:17.840
within you, that such a happening
can happen in such a very short time,

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:23.520
to people like us, who, after all,
are not that spiritually pure,

00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:25.600
that spiritually evolved.

00:02:25.600 --> 00:02:29.120
But it has been written
in very ancient scriptures,

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:33.120
that this residual consciousness
within each of us,

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:39.440
which is called Kundalini,
spontaneously raises

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:44.714
in the 'darshan' of the Adi Shakti.

00:02:44.714 --> 00:02:50.240
'Adi' means primordial,
'Shakti' means power.

00:02:50.240 --> 00:02:54.320
Our spiritual potential
can be awakened spontaneously

00:02:54.320 --> 00:02:59.840
and effortlessly in the presence
of the One who is the Divine Mother.

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:03.520
Now we are thousands of people
all over the continents.

00:03:03.520 --> 00:03:10.240
We have gone to many, many
various movements, with very many gurus,

00:03:10.240 --> 00:03:15.360
and one or the others,
we have disregarded them, discarded them,

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:20.160
because they didn't offer
what we were actually seeking,

00:03:20.160 --> 00:03:24.480
that is a genuine happening,
not 'blah, blah, blah',

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:30.400
not spiritual lectures,
but something happening inside.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:36.560
And something which had to fit
with the teachings of Lord Krishna,

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:39.760
with the teachings of Jesus Christ,

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:47.600
with the teachings of all
the great masters.

00:03:47.600 --> 00:03:50.880
You see, it's like being
in a junky market,

00:03:50.880 --> 00:03:54.960
where all the junk
is priced very expensively.

00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:59.840
And there is somewhere a stand
where genuine pearls are on display,

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:02.080
and they are offered free.

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:06.480
Now, how are the customers
going to believe that the pearls are genuine?

00:04:06.480 --> 00:04:10.480
Now, that's going to be
your problem maybe this evening.

00:04:10.480 --> 00:04:17.440
But give yourself a chance to think
that this can happen to you.

00:04:17.440 --> 00:04:22.320
None of us were more worthy
than anyone else

00:04:22.320 --> 00:04:29.280
of entering into this realm
of collective consciousness,

00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:30.800
which is open by Sahaja Yoga.

00:04:30.800 --> 00:04:36.240
Yet, it did happen.
So it might happen to you also.

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:42.000
The only thing which is required from you
is just to sit relaxed,

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:49.280
not to accept, not to reject,

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:58.160
to silence the mind a little bit
if possible, and to be open.

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:53.722
It's all right. It's all right.
I'll walk this side.

00:05:53.722 --> 00:05:54.800
If there is a custom
to thank your own children,

00:05:57.760 --> 00:06:05.440
who are anxious to share
whatever they have achieved,

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:11.040
I would like to thank
my Sahaja Yogis children,

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:14.880
who have been giving Me this idea,

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:26.640
who have arranged this program
in this beautiful hall.

00:06:26.640 --> 00:06:36.320
As now Gregoire was telling you,
that it has to be free.

00:06:36.320 --> 00:06:42.240
The grace of God
cannot be purchased.

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:46.320
What can you pay for it?

00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:53.200
If anybody had taken any money,
he has insulted

00:06:53.200 --> 00:07:02.400
the very basis of spiritual life.

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:07.840
I do not know in these modern times,
where everything they sell.

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:13.840
So, people think they can also
sell God and be saved.

00:07:19.040 --> 00:07:32.480
If you see the lives of very great prophets
like Mohammed, Nanaka, Kabir

00:07:32.480 --> 00:07:38.720
they did not sell what they had to be.

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:46.000
Even Christ, He had to take a hunter
in his hand

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:52.480
and beat the people who were trying
to sell things outside the church.

00:07:52.480 --> 00:07:54.480
They are not selling God.

00:07:54.480 --> 00:08:01.440
But even to use the premises
of God's worship like a market,

00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:10.000
He could not bear it.
It was too much to see.

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:15.200
So you cannot pay for it.
That's very sure.

00:08:15.200 --> 00:08:22.240
And think of it, what can you pay
for the grace of God?

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:33.040
The second thing about Self-realization
is to understand mentally

00:08:33.040 --> 00:08:37.200
that you cannot put in effort about it.

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:40.320
What is the Self-realization actually?

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:48.080
It's the last breakthrough
of human beings into your own being,

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:50.880
into your own evolutionary process.

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:56.160
You reach a goal
where you become yourself.

00:08:56.160 --> 00:09:06.960
As I say, this cord here,
it has been created as instrument.

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:12.480
To make it act as itself,
it has to be put to the mains.

00:09:12.480 --> 00:09:18.080
In the same way,
we are to be put to the mains

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:24.240
to know what we are,
and what we are supposed to do,

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:28.320
and to have our fulfilment.

00:09:28.320 --> 00:09:34.000
This gap of breakthrough
has to be spontaneous,

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:39.920
because it is a living process
like a sprouting of a seed.

00:09:39.920 --> 00:09:44.240
You cannot make a seed sprout by orders,

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:47.840
or by standing on your head,
or doing any Hatha Yoga.

00:09:47.840 --> 00:09:51.600
You cannot make the seed germinate.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:56.400
If there is a seed within you,
and the germinating power

00:09:56.400 --> 00:10:04.000
has to sprout by itself,
it has to be spontaneous.

00:10:04.000 --> 00:10:07.440
If you understand the meaning
of the living process,

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:13.280
it is responsible for bringing you
from amoeba stage to this human stage,

00:10:13.280 --> 00:10:17.680
for which you need not do anything,

00:10:17.680 --> 00:10:23.840
you should also know that this
is the job of God and not you.

00:10:23.840 --> 00:10:29.520
The God Almighty is going to work out
your spontaneous rebirth.

00:10:29.520 --> 00:10:34.320
It is through his grace
you are going to do it.

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:38.160
It is your own capability,
your own stability

00:10:38.160 --> 00:10:43.440
and your own achievements
within yourself, that you are going to do.

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:51.920
You have achieved your human stage
after passing through many phases of lives.

00:10:51.920 --> 00:10:57.840
And today you are here
to receive that grace in yourself,

00:10:57.840 --> 00:11:05.200
and to achieve that what has been promised
in all the scriptures.

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:09.760
There cannot be any quarrel
as far as the truth is concerned.

00:11:09.760 --> 00:11:15.360
Because truth is one
and it is described in many different languages.

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:18.880
But it's described the same,
in all of them,

00:11:18.880 --> 00:11:28.240
and it's prophesied that one day will come,
that you will be convinced of it.

00:11:28.240 --> 00:11:35.200
So far, it could not be done en-masse.

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:38.800
It could be achieved
by only very few individuals.

00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:45.280
Because it is the way
evolution always goes on.

00:11:45.280 --> 00:11:55.200
First a small fish comes out of the sea,
touches the shores, becomes a reptile.

00:11:55.200 --> 00:12:01.440
And then few more,
and then all sorts of fishes followed.

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:05.596
In the same way
your evolution is going to work out.

00:12:05.596 --> 00:12:08.800
For very few achieved it,
they described it.

00:12:08.800 --> 00:12:11.760
But for you, it was an activity
which you can't understand

00:12:11.760 --> 00:12:13.600
what they were talking about.

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:17.760
Because they were born at a place
which was much higher than you,

00:12:17.760 --> 00:12:22.160
say on the 10th storey,
and you were just on the ground level.

00:12:22.160 --> 00:12:25.040
How will you know
what they are talking about?

00:12:25.040 --> 00:12:28.800
So it is necessary that you should rise
at least to the fourth storey,

00:12:28.800 --> 00:12:32.560
to know that there is
something beyond it.

00:12:32.560 --> 00:12:36.400
But when I talk about the beyond,
every religion talks about it.

00:12:36.400 --> 00:12:40.560
Everybody talks about the beyond.
Everybody talks about his name.

00:12:40.560 --> 00:12:43.920
When, today, I was discussing
the book with Gregoire,

00:12:43.920 --> 00:12:46.240
he said, "Mother, they are going to pick up
all the words.

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:52.921
They are going to talk the same way
as you are talking".

00:12:52.921 --> 00:12:52.938
I said, "Really?"

00:12:52.938 --> 00:12:54.080
He said, "Really, yes.
Whatever they can pick up,

00:12:54.080 --> 00:12:56.000
they have reached out
from all the scriptures

00:12:56.000 --> 00:13:02.155
and they have talked the same way
as you are talking".

00:13:02.155 --> 00:13:05.200
Then what should I do?

00:13:05.200 --> 00:13:12.560
How am I to tell them
that where you are, you cannot talk.

00:13:12.560 --> 00:13:15.440
They are very subtle
and they know how to put in the circle.

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:25.120
They know how to propagate.
And they know how to pass.

00:13:25.120 --> 00:13:29.426
The other day, I met somebody
who was very right-handed man

00:13:29.426 --> 00:13:32.160
whom we saved from somebody
who was a wicked man,

00:13:32.160 --> 00:13:34.640
out of your country also.

00:13:34.640 --> 00:13:37.200
And this right-handed man
then came to Sahaja Yoga

00:13:37.200 --> 00:13:39.680
because he wanted something for himself.

00:13:39.680 --> 00:13:42.320
He said, "I have done too much
for this man and I have got nothing.

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:44.400
So I must have something for myself".

00:13:44.400 --> 00:13:47.040
So he came down to Sahaja Yoga.

00:13:47.040 --> 00:13:48.400
And then he told me the trick.

00:13:48.400 --> 00:13:53.200
He said, "This man has confessed to me
that if you pay,

00:13:53.200 --> 00:13:56.720
then the people have
a feeling of involvement.

00:13:56.720 --> 00:14:00.840
If you pay money, say for a picture,
it may not be very good.

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:04.080
You go and see the picture
and see to the end of it,

00:14:04.080 --> 00:14:05.440
because you have paid for it".

00:14:05.440 --> 00:14:07.520
That's the psychology
human beings have.

00:14:07.520 --> 00:14:13.040
And that's how it pays in a double.

00:14:13.040 --> 00:14:18.000
But to a seeker of truth,
he does not pay for it.

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:20.400
Let them take away your money.

00:14:20.400 --> 00:14:25.040
Let them take away all that is
superficial, transitory.

00:14:25.040 --> 00:14:28.480
But they have to give you something
of eternal life.

00:14:29.280 --> 00:14:35.760
He doesn't pay off the seeker,
neither the ones who are a facade with that.

00:14:35.760 --> 00:14:38.800
They are the real ones.

00:14:38.800 --> 00:14:42.960
It's going to be a very dangerous game
for such people, no doubt.

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:48.080
And also for the seekers
if they do not wake up in right time,

00:14:48.080 --> 00:14:55.360
and understand that reality
is to be felt and experienced within ourselves.

00:14:55.360 --> 00:15:01.040
And it is not to be just brainwashed
in our heads, that this is the reality.

00:15:01.040 --> 00:15:05.280
It is to be actualized in our experience.

00:15:05.280 --> 00:15:09.120
If it is not so, just discard anybody.

00:15:09.120 --> 00:15:14.000
Anybody who comes in the name of God
or Jesus or anyone of them,

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:18.080
they have nothing to do
with these great incarnations

00:15:18.080 --> 00:15:21.760
who came on this earth to evolve you,

00:15:21.760 --> 00:15:31.200
and to bring you to this point
that you are just ready to achieve your goal.

00:15:31.200 --> 00:15:35.040
When I tell you about the Kundalini,

00:15:35.040 --> 00:15:42.480
you can see here, in the picture we have shown,
in that triangular thing,

00:15:42.480 --> 00:15:46.720
is the Kundalini,
is the residual consciousness,

00:15:46.720 --> 00:15:55.120
placed by nature of God Almighty,
it just has to be put to the mains.

00:15:55.120 --> 00:15:56.800
It's all done for you.

00:15:56.800 --> 00:16:01.120
The whole thing is prepared within you
when you became a human being.

00:16:01.120 --> 00:16:06.480
The fifth center developed
when you raised your head from animal stage

00:16:06.480 --> 00:16:08.160
and you started looking up.

00:16:08.160 --> 00:16:14.000
That is the stage at which a man
became a human being,

00:16:14.000 --> 00:16:17.280
from chimpanzee, you can say.

00:16:17.280 --> 00:16:22.400
Then the higher stage is the sixth stage
when Christ came on this earth.

00:16:22.400 --> 00:16:26.240
That is the sixth center
where Christ resides

00:16:26.240 --> 00:16:34.400
and He came on this earth to show you
what Lord Krishna has preached throughout,

00:16:34.400 --> 00:16:38.800
that it cannot be killed,
it cannot be blown off,

00:16:38.800 --> 00:16:42.640
it cannot be finished and destroyed

00:16:42.640 --> 00:16:49.360
and that eternal life was proved by Christ
at this stage.

00:16:49.360 --> 00:16:55.760
All the great saints, or we can say
the prophets who came on this earth to teach us,

00:16:55.760 --> 00:17:02.400
have been the manifestation
of the Primordial Masters,

00:17:02.400 --> 00:17:05.200
who came on this earth to guide us

00:17:05.200 --> 00:17:09.360
and to tell us what we should do
to stabilize ourselves,

00:17:09.360 --> 00:17:12.960
to be ready to get our Realisation,

00:17:12.960 --> 00:17:20.320
what is our style of life
that is going to help us

00:17:20.320 --> 00:17:22.320
to be able to manage.

00:17:22.320 --> 00:17:30.720
And these people appeared
at this green centre,

00:17:30.720 --> 00:17:37.840
which is built up to receive
and carry sub-plexuses or sub-patterns,

00:17:37.840 --> 00:17:46.160
and these are the ten sub-plexuses
which represent our ten masters.

00:17:46.160 --> 00:17:52.240
These have been supported,
fully supported by all the prophets

00:17:52.240 --> 00:17:54.400
who came on this earth.

00:17:54.400 --> 00:17:58.400
They talked about it
because they had to stabilize.

00:17:58.400 --> 00:18:01.520
A prophet came on this earth to stabilize,

00:18:01.520 --> 00:18:06.320
to give you the idea of inner religion,

00:18:06.320 --> 00:18:13.520
the stabilizing points within you
by which you will learn how to balance yourself.

00:18:13.520 --> 00:18:17.760
Like when you have to climb up,
you must also know how to balance,

00:18:17.760 --> 00:18:21.200
otherwise you will go more
on the left or more on the right,

00:18:21.200 --> 00:18:22.800
and there will be a problem.

00:18:22.800 --> 00:18:27.040
So these prophets came on this earth
to teach you how to stabilize,

00:18:27.040 --> 00:18:32.320
and they are all set in
in your own stomach, they are there.

00:18:32.320 --> 00:18:38.320
They exist there but in most of the cases
they are not active.

00:18:38.320 --> 00:18:42.400
Once they are active,
nobody has to tell you "Don't do".

00:18:42.400 --> 00:18:45.200
There is no need
because if you try to do anything,

00:18:45.200 --> 00:18:51.520
you just cannot do it,
you will start vomiting.

00:18:51.520 --> 00:18:54.800
It is so automatically built in by depth

00:18:54.800 --> 00:18:58.400
but as they are not yet
awakened within you,

00:18:58.400 --> 00:19:00.000
you can do whatever you like.

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:04.960
It is your freedom,
so-called freedom, as I call it,

00:19:04.960 --> 00:19:07.040
to destroy yourself.

00:19:07.040 --> 00:19:09.280
It is there when they
are enlightened within you.

00:19:09.280 --> 00:19:11.680
For example, Moses was one of them.

00:19:11.680 --> 00:19:14.400
They were mainly ten people
who came on this earth.

00:19:15.520 --> 00:19:19.280
The same essence, the same personality,
you can say,

00:19:19.280 --> 00:19:23.920
took their birth in different times
to guide us all throughout,

00:19:23.920 --> 00:19:28.880
how to be completely silent.

00:19:28.880 --> 00:19:31.280
Now there are six different centres,

00:19:31.280 --> 00:19:36.800
and if I am to explain them all,
it would be a very lengthy lecture,

00:19:36.800 --> 00:19:40.960
which I don't think we have
so much time for in this one lecture.

00:19:40.960 --> 00:19:47.760
But in any case, I would like to tell you
another very important centre.

00:19:47.760 --> 00:19:52.920
It is placed at that red coloured one.

00:19:52.920 --> 00:19:57.440
It is the first one
which is called as the Mooladhara Chakra,

00:19:57.440 --> 00:20:01.760
meaning the centre of the root,

00:20:01.760 --> 00:20:06.636
or you can say,
the support of the root.

00:20:06.636 --> 00:20:11.600
The support of the root,
the root is the Kundalini,

00:20:11.600 --> 00:20:17.040
and the support of the root
is this particular centre.

00:20:17.040 --> 00:20:22.320
And that's why this centre
is a very important centre to Me now

00:20:22.320 --> 00:20:26.160
and this is the centre of innocence.

00:20:26.160 --> 00:20:32.240
When this universe was created,
first innocence was created.

00:20:32.240 --> 00:20:36.240
Sin was not created first,
it was innocence that was created.

00:20:36.240 --> 00:20:40.960
And this is the first centre within us
which exists as innocence.

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:47.120
And the deity on this,
is the deity which is

00:20:47.120 --> 00:20:49.840
the embodiment of innocence within us.

00:20:49.840 --> 00:20:53.680
But when we try to fight our innocence,

00:20:53.680 --> 00:20:59.360
and we try to get out of our innocence,
this deity sleeps off.

00:20:59.360 --> 00:21:03.920
Once this deity sleeps off, we can do
whatever we like with our innocence.

00:21:03.920 --> 00:21:11.280
We can go to any extent of wrongdoing,
any kind of sins. Nothing can happen.

00:21:11.280 --> 00:21:16.400
When this is awakened, immediately
you realize there is a problem,

00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:20.960
and this problem is because I am running away
from my innocence,

00:21:20.960 --> 00:21:23.600
and innocence is not something to run from.

00:21:23.600 --> 00:21:29.200
Now it is a very, very abstract thing
that I am talking about

00:21:29.200 --> 00:21:32.880
which you may find is
something out of the blue.

00:21:32.880 --> 00:21:34.457
But these are all within you.

00:21:34.457 --> 00:21:34.476
You will be amazed.

00:21:34.476 --> 00:21:37.920
All these centres are placed within you,

00:21:37.920 --> 00:21:40.880
except for the red one,
all the rest are placed

00:21:40.880 --> 00:21:45.360
in your backbone
and within your spinal cords.

00:21:45.360 --> 00:21:50.480
The first part of the brain
is on one side, left side and right side

00:21:50.480 --> 00:21:58.560
as I showed you,
is made of three powers coming through.

00:21:58.560 --> 00:22:02.880
The first power that is shown
is on the left-hand side,

00:22:02.880 --> 00:22:05.280
which is shown in the black.

00:22:05.280 --> 00:22:08.320
It's the power by which you exist.

00:22:08.320 --> 00:22:13.600
And when it manifests within you,
it manifests outside on the physical plane,

00:22:13.600 --> 00:22:16.000
as the left sympathetic nervous system,

00:22:20.880 --> 00:22:24.240
and is expressed as our existence.

00:22:24.240 --> 00:22:28.240
If you see on the right-hand side
is the second power

00:22:28.240 --> 00:22:35.440
which is in the yellow colour,
is the colour of the sun, you can say.

00:22:35.440 --> 00:22:40.160
And is also called as Sun channel.

00:22:40.160 --> 00:22:46.640
This line exists within us,
helps us in our creativity.

00:22:46.640 --> 00:22:50.880
We create, we think about it,
through this line.

00:22:50.880 --> 00:22:55.920
It also creates this body
and also maintains this body.

00:22:55.920 --> 00:23:02.320
Plus, it also gives us power
to create things for the future

00:23:02.320 --> 00:23:06.400
and this we call as
the supraconscious area,

00:23:07.360 --> 00:23:09.040
which takes us to our future.

00:23:09.040 --> 00:23:12.880
When we think about our future
and we plan about our future,

00:23:12.880 --> 00:23:17.680
this is another kind of energy
that flows within us.

00:23:17.680 --> 00:23:21.120
These are the undercurrents
I am telling you, which exist within us.

00:23:21.120 --> 00:23:24.160
Now you don't have to believe Me
because I am telling you.

00:23:24.160 --> 00:23:26.240
But this is a hypothesis for you.

00:23:26.240 --> 00:23:33.200
As a scientist you must accept
the hypothesis at the outward expression of it.

00:23:33.200 --> 00:23:35.360
But later on, you can experiment within,

00:23:35.360 --> 00:23:38.480
and find for yourself
if these things are true or not.

00:23:39.840 --> 00:23:44.240
Now the middle path,
that is what you call the middle path of Buddha,

00:23:44.240 --> 00:23:47.840
or you can say the central part
of our being

00:23:47.840 --> 00:23:52.320
is a channel which we call
as a Sushumna channel.

00:23:52.320 --> 00:23:58.240
And this channel manifests outside
the parasympathetic nervous system.

00:23:58.240 --> 00:24:00.560
So we have got three channels.

00:24:00.560 --> 00:24:07.840
First the Ida channel which expresses
the left side sympathetic nervous system.

00:24:07.840 --> 00:24:14.400
The right side is the Pingala channel
which expresses

00:24:14.400 --> 00:24:18.240
the right side sympathetic
nervous system.

00:24:18.240 --> 00:24:23.040
And in the centre is the Sushumna channel
which expresses

00:24:23.040 --> 00:24:25.600
the parasympathetic nervous system.

00:24:25.600 --> 00:24:29.280
Now you are not doctors so,
I am telling you a little bit about it.

00:24:29.280 --> 00:24:35.760
And there is, within us,
of course, you know the central nervous system

00:24:35.760 --> 00:24:38.240
by which we are conscious of everything.

00:24:38.240 --> 00:24:39.760
But we are not fully conscious.

00:24:39.760 --> 00:24:43.200
For example we are not conscious
of our centres within us.

00:24:43.200 --> 00:24:46.320
After Realisation only
you can become conscious.

00:24:46.320 --> 00:24:49.280
You can start feeling them
and you will start knowing

00:24:49.280 --> 00:24:53.440
where is the obstruction,
where is the thing and what is working.

00:24:53.440 --> 00:24:56.480
After Self-realization only
you know yourself,

00:24:56.480 --> 00:24:58.640
means you know your instrument within

00:24:58.640 --> 00:25:01.920
and what position is the problem,
where is the Kundalini,

00:25:01.920 --> 00:25:05.840
where it is rising,
how it is falling down, how far it has gone.

00:25:05.840 --> 00:25:09.600
Everything you will only know,
when you have got Realisation

00:25:09.600 --> 00:25:13.680
and you will have dimension
in which you can feel yourself.

00:25:13.680 --> 00:25:17.920
And also you can feel others,
in the way,

00:25:17.920 --> 00:25:20.640
I always give a very simple example.

00:25:20.640 --> 00:25:24.480
Like you are all pearls
and the pearls&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:25:24.480 --> 00:25:27.680
are stringed together to one string.

00:25:27.680 --> 00:25:30.720
But just now, you are separate.

00:25:30.720 --> 00:25:35.920
If you are stringed together,
put on to the string which connects each other,

00:25:35.920 --> 00:25:38.400
then you jump into a new awareness,

00:25:38.400 --> 00:25:41.040
where you start feeling each other.

00:25:41.040 --> 00:25:46.640
For example now, this light,
if you put on this lamp, it comes to light

00:25:46.640 --> 00:25:48.400
because it is in the subtle.

00:25:48.400 --> 00:25:51.920
But if you are not in the subtle,
then the light will go down.

00:25:51.920 --> 00:25:56.160
In the same way, if you come
into the subtle by Self-realization,

00:25:56.160 --> 00:25:57.920
then the connection takes place like this.

00:25:58.560 --> 00:26:02.560
You absolutely become one
with the All-pervading subtle Power

00:26:02.560 --> 00:26:07.200
which is being described
by all these great scriptures.

00:26:07.200 --> 00:26:10.080
It happens to you spontaneously.

00:26:10.080 --> 00:26:16.236
I was telling you a little bit
about the parasympathetic and the sympathetic.

00:26:16.236 --> 00:26:20.860
Now sympathetic nervous system is the system
which we use when we are in emergency.

00:26:20.860 --> 00:26:26.848
For example, I have seen a lion,
I start running.

00:26:26.848 --> 00:26:27.840
I start running,
my heart starts pumping fast.

00:26:27.840 --> 00:26:30.240
Now this is the sympathetic we are using.

00:26:30.240 --> 00:26:38.160
But the same sympathetic
can be used for increasing the rate of heart.

00:26:38.160 --> 00:26:44.080
For decreasing the rate of heart,
you find automatically, spontaneously,

00:26:44.080 --> 00:26:47.120
when you stop after some time,
it slows the heart.

00:26:47.120 --> 00:26:50.720
That is done by parasympathetic.

00:26:51.760 --> 00:26:56.320
The left sympathetic nervous system
caters to our emotional side

00:26:56.320 --> 00:26:58.080
and our emotional attachment,

00:26:58.080 --> 00:27:04.000
and right side to our thinking
and our physical being.

00:27:04.000 --> 00:27:07.360
Now this is the way
you are placed within yourself.

00:27:07.360 --> 00:27:12.160
I will not describe all the chakras,
all the centres, but they are there.

00:27:12.160 --> 00:27:16.687
Now you may say,
in the Bible, where do you find it?

00:27:16.687 --> 00:27:19.920
In the Bible, it is said,
"I will appear before you like tongues of flame".

00:27:19.920 --> 00:27:22.400
Now which priest can explain them?

00:27:22.400 --> 00:27:25.520
If they are not Realised souls,
if they have not been inside,

00:27:25.520 --> 00:27:31.269
they have not seen them.
How will they know?

00:27:31.269 --> 00:27:32.400
Kabira has talked about those.

00:27:34.000 --> 00:27:36.000
He has described chakras after chakras.

00:27:36.000 --> 00:27:40.320
Adi Shankaracharya, of course,&nbsp;

00:27:40.320 --> 00:27:40.960
nothing to say

00:27:40.960 --> 00:27:44.796
because the whole thing
is nothing but how to awaken the Kundalini.

00:27:44.796 --> 00:27:49.440
Now the mistake in Kundalini awakening
is that, as I said,

00:27:49.440 --> 00:27:51.440
they pick up everything, you see.

00:27:51.440 --> 00:27:56.320
If you see a diamond,
you can make an artificial diamond.

00:27:56.320 --> 00:28:02.000
If you see a real bird,
you can also make an artificial bird.

00:28:02.880 --> 00:28:05.040
You can make everything artificial.

00:28:05.040 --> 00:28:05.627
In the same way,
these horrible people

00:28:05.627 --> 00:28:13.520
have also made the Kundalini
itself absolutely artificial.

00:28:13.520 --> 00:28:15.120
Because they have read about it.

00:28:15.120 --> 00:28:18.635
Now they started finding,
"Where is this Kundalini? Let us try to find out".

00:28:18.635 --> 00:28:22.720
They exploit you for their own good.

00:28:22.720 --> 00:28:26.880
Now you cannot find that,
it's not possible.

00:28:26.880 --> 00:28:29.040
It's a very precious thing
and that's why its support

00:28:29.040 --> 00:28:33.680
is sitting down there,
looking after the Kundalini.

00:28:33.680 --> 00:28:38.640
Now imagine, the idea is so funny,
so shocking

00:28:38.640 --> 00:28:43.040
that these people—
I would not say, as a Mother,

00:28:43.040 --> 00:28:44.960
to condemn them completely,
in the beginning,

00:28:44.960 --> 00:28:47.200
maybe for the mistake
of their forefathers.

00:28:47.200 --> 00:28:50.880
It might be, they might have seen something
in that area,

00:28:50.880 --> 00:28:55.920
which is the red chakra
which controls the sex.

00:28:55.920 --> 00:29:00.640
And they might have seen a part
of the deity which has got a trunk,

00:29:00.640 --> 00:29:04.720
and might have concluded that,
"This is the Kundalini".

00:29:04.720 --> 00:29:07.760
I give them the benefit of the doubt, maybe.

00:29:07.760 --> 00:29:11.040
And that's how they concluded
that if you excite the sex

00:29:11.040 --> 00:29:15.355
you can get the Kundalini awakening,
which is absolutely wrong.

00:29:15.355 --> 00:29:17.600
It's just the opposition of what it is.

00:29:17.600 --> 00:29:20.480
Don't be shocked! It's a fact.

00:29:20.480 --> 00:29:23.040
If you try to do
this kind of a nonsense,

00:29:23.040 --> 00:29:26.400
it is something like,
there the mother is sitting down.

00:29:26.400 --> 00:29:28.640
She is the mother who is going
to give you the birth,

00:29:28.640 --> 00:29:34.000
this Kundalini is there, sitting down,
waiting for all your lives, till today,

00:29:34.000 --> 00:29:35.440
to give you the rebirth.

00:29:35.440 --> 00:29:40.800
And here you are,
putting sex on your own Mother.

00:29:40.800 --> 00:29:44.640
What? What is worse than this?
How insulting it is.

00:29:44.640 --> 00:29:45.760
Just think of it.

00:29:45.760 --> 00:29:50.611
And such an absurd thing is done
by these people

00:29:50.611 --> 00:29:51.440
who call themselves Tantrikas
and Matrikas

00:29:51.440 --> 00:29:53.917
and now they do all kinds of things,
and they are selling them

00:29:53.917 --> 00:29:56.160
in the market very nicely.

00:29:56.160 --> 00:29:59.600
You'll be amazed,
there is somebody now here in London,

00:30:00.320 --> 00:30:00.960
they told Me.

00:30:00.960 --> 00:30:04.400
They started with about 30 people
in the hall.

00:30:04.400 --> 00:30:06.640
And they said,
"You have to take off all your clothes

00:30:06.640 --> 00:30:09.360
and you just dance and you're nude".

00:30:09.360 --> 00:30:13.680
So, next day they were 60.

00:30:13.680 --> 00:30:17.840
Now there are so many people
that they have to hire bigger and bigger halls.

00:30:19.200 --> 00:30:23.511
Now if you ask people to come down,
take off your clothes and dance,

00:30:23.511 --> 00:30:26.310
you see, they should deny you
and they should.

00:30:26.310 --> 00:30:28.000
Then they will have these people.

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:32.160
Let them have these people,
who are filling their pockets nicely,

00:30:32.160 --> 00:30:36.560
and befooling you,
just making you dance, exhaust,

00:30:36.560 --> 00:30:39.680
making you sinful
and think they're doing good.

00:30:39.680 --> 00:30:41.280
That's the best way they can do it.

00:30:41.280 --> 00:30:44.320
Because there must be some weakness
about people also,

00:30:44.320 --> 00:30:47.040
that they are so foolish
to accept such a thing,

00:30:47.040 --> 00:30:49.440
that dancing naked,
you could get reward.

00:30:50.000 --> 00:30:57.360
In India, or in any poor country,
do you think they are going to achieve God

00:30:57.360 --> 00:30:58.240
by doing that?

00:30:58.240 --> 00:31:03.920
Or dancing on the Oxford street,
do you think they can achieve God?

00:31:03.920 --> 00:31:05.520
Use your brain.

00:31:05.520 --> 00:31:10.160
How can God be that mad
to create such a situation for you,

00:31:10.720 --> 00:31:13.120
and make you lose your Realisation?

00:31:13.120 --> 00:31:13.440
No.

00:31:13.440 --> 00:31:18.800
You have to be baptized
at the point that He is trying to bring us to.

00:31:18.800 --> 00:31:21.760
And it has to come up
through your fontanel bone,

00:31:21.760 --> 00:31:23.360
where it should open up,

00:31:23.360 --> 00:31:26.320
and you must get into
the All-pervading Power.

00:31:26.320 --> 00:31:30.080
You have to become that subtle being
and that is what you have to achieve.

00:31:30.080 --> 00:31:34.880
You do not achieve it,
if you are not a Self-realized soul.

00:31:34.880 --> 00:31:36.880
Now, say, for example,
if somebody says,

00:31:36.880 --> 00:31:39.360
"Mother, you must give
my son the Realisation".

00:31:39.360 --> 00:31:40.480
I cannot.

00:31:40.480 --> 00:31:42.480
I cannot say that I can give.

00:31:42.480 --> 00:31:44.640
If it has to work, it will work.

00:31:44.640 --> 00:31:48.320
If it does not work out—
before, on my own children,

00:31:48.320 --> 00:31:51.440
I cannot say that they have been given
the Realisation.

00:31:51.440 --> 00:31:54.320
It is the genuine thing
that works in you.

00:31:54.320 --> 00:31:56.800
Maybe there is a problem
in one of your chakras.

00:31:56.800 --> 00:31:59.600
Maybe emotionally you are ruined,
emotionally you are tired,

00:31:59.600 --> 00:32:01.440
maybe it is the children
who have gone wrong.

00:32:01.440 --> 00:32:02.640
Something has gone wrong with you.

00:32:02.640 --> 00:32:05.440
You have gone to the wrong guru
or something like that has happened.

00:32:05.440 --> 00:32:08.640
The Kundalini is not raising.

00:32:08.640 --> 00:32:09.520
She knows.

00:32:09.520 --> 00:32:11.920
She is a tape-recorder
of your subconscious,

00:32:11.920 --> 00:32:12.960
and she is your mother.

00:32:12.960 --> 00:32:17.040
And she will be the first to jump up
and to give you that Realisation

00:32:17.040 --> 00:32:19.440
because she is waiting for this.

00:32:19.440 --> 00:32:22.240
But it may not work.

00:32:22.240 --> 00:32:24.480
You may be a very egoistical person.

00:32:25.120 --> 00:32:29.280
The whole brain might be covered
in this yellow stuff, which is the ego.

00:32:29.280 --> 00:32:32.720
Or maybe you are possessed,
and the whole thing is covered in the black,

00:32:32.720 --> 00:32:35.200
which is the superego.

00:32:35.200 --> 00:32:37.440
You might be a person
with drug and chemical habits

00:32:37.440 --> 00:32:40.160
and have taken all the drugs
in your body

00:32:40.160 --> 00:32:42.800
and there is something wrong
on your physical plane.

00:32:42.800 --> 00:32:48.114
Maybe something has happened to you.
It may not rise.

00:32:48.114 --> 00:32:48.160
It must be cleansed somehow.
We'll work it out.

00:32:48.160 --> 00:32:54.920
We can only say that we can work it out,
because it's a genuine thing.

00:32:55.600 --> 00:33:00.000
It is not giving you a false thing.

00:33:07.040 --> 00:33:11.600
You cannot just foolishly say that,

00:33:11.600 --> 00:33:17.280
"All right, you pay two hundred dollars,
and I will give you a mantra

00:33:17.280 --> 00:33:20.640
and immediately you become that".

00:33:20.640 --> 00:33:23.440
This is an imposture. Think about it.

00:33:23.440 --> 00:33:32.000
How can someone just say,
"You can just become something special"?

00:33:32.000 --> 00:33:36.080
Maybe you are going on the left-hand side
to the collective subconscious

00:33:36.080 --> 00:33:39.440
or go the right-hand side
to the collective supra-conscious.

00:33:39.440 --> 00:33:42.000
Maybe you are possessed by something.

00:33:42.000 --> 00:33:49.609
Maybe there is some sort of possession
that is working in you

00:33:49.609 --> 00:33:49.680
and you feel you have
become something special.

00:33:49.680 --> 00:33:53.760
So you have to remember that
a Realized soul

00:33:53.760 --> 00:33:56.960
is a person who knows
about his own chakras.

00:33:56.960 --> 00:33:58.960
Even a small little child
of two years old,

00:33:58.960 --> 00:34:01.760
will be able to tell you
where is the catch about it.

00:34:01.760 --> 00:34:05.280
You are that evolved.

00:34:05.280 --> 00:34:11.520
It's a subjective knowledge that becomes
a part and parcel of your own being.

00:34:11.520 --> 00:34:16.320
Like if you can be enlightened,
you can see yourself enough.

00:34:16.320 --> 00:34:20.400
You have got eyes to see.
You don't have to ask others.

00:34:20.400 --> 00:34:27.440
You just see them
because you have eyes to know.

00:34:27.440 --> 00:34:29.760
Enlightenment means this.

00:34:29.760 --> 00:34:34.880
And not enlightenment that somebody comes
and puts a little spark in your head.

00:34:34.880 --> 00:34:38.960
They will all end up
as mad people or broken hearts.

00:34:38.960 --> 00:34:43.345
They are already
having such problems.

00:34:43.345 --> 00:34:47.191
In Caxton Hall,
at least fifty percent of people are like that.

00:34:47.191 --> 00:34:49.431
They are exhausted in their pursuit.

00:34:49.431 --> 00:34:53.680
They are exhausted in their brain,
exhausted in their heart.

00:34:53.680 --> 00:34:58.692
Poor people have worked day in and day out
for all this.

00:34:58.692 --> 00:34:59.600
There was a German girl who came to Me.

00:34:59.600 --> 00:35:01.040
And she's so exhausted now.

00:35:01.040 --> 00:35:05.120
She said, "Mother, I have given up
all my property, all my money, everything.

00:35:05.120 --> 00:35:07.760
I am broke, now.
I am finished!

00:35:07.760 --> 00:35:10.480
And at this stage,
I discovered that, oh God,

00:35:10.480 --> 00:35:12.320
I have been all wrong".

00:35:12.320 --> 00:35:17.200
I said, "What happened with your brain?
Where did you leave it?"

00:35:17.200 --> 00:35:19.920
She said, "No, they have real reasons
doing that.

00:35:19.920 --> 00:35:22.000
They make you surrender yourself
in such a way

00:35:22.000 --> 00:35:25.200
that you surrender your wisdom", she said.

00:35:25.200 --> 00:35:30.872
But why not surrender to your wisdom
by understanding it

00:35:30.872 --> 00:35:32.480
through your brain, first of all?

00:35:32.480 --> 00:35:36.640
So I ask you on rationality,
that you understand

00:35:36.640 --> 00:35:40.560
that reality means that
you have to face it.

00:35:40.560 --> 00:35:41.760
You have to do it.

00:35:41.760 --> 00:35:44.560
You should have your own powers manifested.

00:35:44.560 --> 00:35:50.000
What is there if I show you some powers
from here sitting down?

00:36:00.000 --> 00:36:02.400
Will God really do that?

00:36:02.400 --> 00:36:08.960
Is that the way to recognize
our spiritual evolved personality?

00:36:08.960 --> 00:36:10.640
Think about it.

00:36:10.640 --> 00:36:13.591
So what is the way?
How are we to do it?

00:36:13.591 --> 00:36:21.360
It's our love being exposed to God
and to our heart.

00:36:21.360 --> 00:36:24.720
Then another thing,
it is not like an advertisement.

00:36:24.720 --> 00:36:25.680
One has to be deep.

00:36:25.680 --> 00:36:27.040
You have to be deeper.

00:36:27.040 --> 00:36:29.520
If you are superficial,
it will not work.

00:36:29.520 --> 00:36:32.560
You have to be deep about it
and understand with all reverence,

00:36:33.280 --> 00:36:36.640
that it is a thing that happens to you.

00:36:36.640 --> 00:36:38.960
But you have to maintain it.

00:36:38.960 --> 00:36:47.200
Even if you could give a light
in a proper lamp,

00:36:47.200 --> 00:36:49.120
still you have to look after it.

00:36:49.920 --> 00:37:06.640
In the same way, spiritual life grows.

00:37:06.640 --> 00:37:08.640
It's not a question of faith.

00:37:08.640 --> 00:37:11.280
But you become somebody else, no doubt.

00:37:11.280 --> 00:37:14.400
But you are still a child
and you have to stabilize

00:37:14.400 --> 00:37:20.080
into the new way of life,
into God, in the kingdom of God.

00:37:20.080 --> 00:37:24.160
We have to rise in the kingdom
of God within ourselves.

00:37:24.160 --> 00:37:26.480
And when you rise
in the kingdom of God,

00:37:26.480 --> 00:37:31.280
you are given the power
of citizenship automatically.

00:37:31.280 --> 00:37:33.040
There is no question about it.

00:37:33.040 --> 00:37:38.720
And what is the power of citizenship,
when you arrive there,

00:37:38.720 --> 00:37:43.440
as the honoured citizen
of God's kingdom?

00:37:43.440 --> 00:37:48.953
The first power you get
is of collective consciousness.

00:37:48.953 --> 00:37:49.520
It's a feeling.

00:37:49.520 --> 00:37:52.000
Now, for example, Me,
I'm sitting before him

00:37:52.000 --> 00:37:54.480
and he is catching his Heart Chakra.

00:37:54.480 --> 00:37:56.560
He is putting his hand
and taking vibrations there,

00:37:56.560 --> 00:37:58.560
because he knows
he's catching on Heart Chakra.

00:37:58.560 --> 00:38:00.080
I don't have to tell him that.

00:38:00.080 --> 00:38:02.240
He knows that
and he doesn't feel bad about it.

00:38:02.240 --> 00:38:05.360
He knows that he's got a problem with that.

00:38:05.360 --> 00:38:08.720
Now, if I tell him,
"Now see the vibrations of this boy?",

00:38:08.720 --> 00:38:11.040
immediately he'll tell you
where is the problem.

00:38:11.040 --> 00:38:12.960
And then he can also correct him.

00:38:12.960 --> 00:38:17.120
He can raise his Kundalini
and can give him Realisation.

00:38:17.120 --> 00:38:19.756
Immediately after,
when it happens to you,

00:38:19.756 --> 00:38:28.925
you can start raising.
It's fantastic. Extremely fantastic.

00:38:28.925 --> 00:38:30.560
Because it is said,
it is the Guru, first of all,

00:38:30.560 --> 00:38:33.680
chooses his disciples,
makes them stand on their heads,

00:38:33.680 --> 00:38:37.760
then puts them hanging in the well,
and does all kinds of horrible things.

00:38:41.360 --> 00:38:50.080
But, the time has come
for the Blossom Time.

00:38:50.080 --> 00:38:53.120
Today is the Blossom Time
and it has to work out.

00:38:53.120 --> 00:38:57.840
If it does not work out,
the creation will lose its own sense.

00:38:57.840 --> 00:39:00.160
It has to be en masse.

00:39:00.160 --> 00:39:02.320
It has to happen to many of them

00:39:02.320 --> 00:39:07.360
so that they accept it
and understand it and they spread it.

00:39:07.360 --> 00:39:09.440
And this has to be this way.

00:39:09.440 --> 00:39:12.880
And that's why today's Sahaja Yoga
is very much different

00:39:12.880 --> 00:39:16.080
from the Sahaja Yoga of earlier times,

00:39:16.080 --> 00:39:28.160
which worked out in the same way,
but worked on few people, not en masse.

00:39:28.160 --> 00:39:41.680
It happened with so many in America.

00:39:41.680 --> 00:39:51.261
And, I must say, in India,
how fast it has clicked with so many.

00:39:51.261 --> 00:39:53.200
In England also,
it should be answered for all of you.

00:39:53.200 --> 00:39:55.120
And it should happen to all of you.

00:39:55.120 --> 00:39:59.760
I will be looking forward
to what's happening for you.

00:39:59.760 --> 00:40:01.040
Enjoy your Self.

00:40:01.040 --> 00:40:04.160
Feel your Self,
the source that is you,

00:40:04.160 --> 00:40:07.120
and you'll realize what you are.

00:40:07.120 --> 00:40:12.480
It is not easy, as I told you,
to tell all about it in such a short time,

00:40:12.480 --> 00:40:17.200
because now I've been speaking
and you know how many years I speak,

00:40:17.200 --> 00:40:19.920
and still every time I speak,
they have said,

00:40:19.920 --> 00:40:22.880
"Mother, there's so much to be learned
about it. It's too much to be learned".

00:40:22.880 --> 00:40:24.880
So, I would just say to be short,

00:40:24.880 --> 00:40:30.601
that as, for, say,
lighting these lights,

00:40:30.601 --> 00:40:31.600
you have to just press the button.
It's so simple.

00:40:31.600 --> 00:40:36.080
But behind it also,
there's a big organization

00:40:36.080 --> 00:40:38.960
and a big coordination of so many people,

00:40:38.960 --> 00:40:42.640
that works out this small happening
of just pressing the button.

00:40:42.640 --> 00:40:44.880
But the whole thing is done, it's built.

00:40:44.880 --> 00:40:47.440
Once it is built in,
you just press the button and you get it.

00:40:47.440 --> 00:40:50.520
You get the TV,
you just press it and you get it.

00:40:50.520 --> 00:40:53.840
It has been done after years of research,

00:40:54.400 --> 00:40:59.360
and years of efforts by people going deeply
into themselves, into meditation

00:40:59.360 --> 00:41:03.840
and finding out what sort of thing we are
and what we should do.

00:41:03.840 --> 00:41:07.273
Even Me, I knew all this
from the day I was born.

00:41:07.273 --> 00:41:10.560
I knew about my mission
and I knew also who I was.

00:41:10.560 --> 00:41:12.080
Everything I knew.

00:41:12.080 --> 00:41:15.920
But I didn't know
how to give en masse thing.

00:41:15.920 --> 00:41:19.600
And I had to get into
the Kundalinis of people

00:41:19.600 --> 00:41:21.520
to find out what was the problem.

00:41:21.520 --> 00:41:24.240
Why? Why the Kundalini did not raise?
What's the problem?

00:41:24.240 --> 00:41:29.016
I had to go through all
the permutations and combinations

00:41:29.016 --> 00:41:29.040
till I was 47 years old.

00:41:29.040 --> 00:41:36.328
And after that,
I found it out and I said,

00:41:36.328 --> 00:41:36.396
"I opened the Sahasrara.
I opened it out and people can work it out".

00:41:36.396 --> 00:41:42.800
And then it started working
and now I've been working for so many years

00:41:42.800 --> 00:41:46.400
and it has been fixed.

00:41:46.400 --> 00:41:51.920
So for you, those who are great thinkers
and analysers,

00:41:51.920 --> 00:41:56.560
please do not start analysing Me,
because that makes it difficult.

00:41:56.560 --> 00:42:01.280
Neither start analysing yourself
because that also makes it difficult.

00:42:01.280 --> 00:42:07.280
So just understand that it is not
through rationality you are going to reach there.

00:42:07.280 --> 00:42:10.800
But through rationality,
you reach a point from where you can see

00:42:10.800 --> 00:42:15.440
that you have to reach that high,
and it just works spontaneously.

00:42:15.440 --> 00:42:18.400
Then your rationality,
you may not use,

00:42:18.400 --> 00:42:23.355
but you will be at a point
where you will be just travelling

00:42:23.355 --> 00:42:25.512
with the force, the flow of your river,

00:42:25.512 --> 00:42:29.680
that is the Kundalini there,
which is just coiled up,

00:42:29.680 --> 00:42:33.760
will rise itself
and you will feel that it happens.

00:42:33.760 --> 00:42:35.360
So what happens?

00:42:35.360 --> 00:42:37.996
It's a very easy and simple thing.

00:42:37.996 --> 00:42:38.960
And how is that happening?

00:42:38.960 --> 00:42:43.760
Another simple thing,
like one candle enlightens another candle.

00:42:43.760 --> 00:42:45.040
It's that simple.

00:42:45.040 --> 00:42:48.880
Because you are that,
you are made specially. You are built in.

00:42:48.880 --> 00:42:52.880
Only thing what happens is
you just pour a little water on your seed,

00:42:52.880 --> 00:42:54.320
and the seed sprouts.

00:42:54.320 --> 00:42:55.680
That's all my job is.

00:42:55.680 --> 00:42:56.720
It's your own seed.

00:42:56.720 --> 00:43:00.560
It's your own Kundalini
and you get your own rights.

00:43:00.560 --> 00:43:04.080
And it is your own right
no matter what you have been.

00:43:04.080 --> 00:43:11.319
So my job is only to pour
a little water of love

00:43:11.319 --> 00:43:11.360
and just to see that it sprouts properly.

00:43:11.360 --> 00:43:15.996
If there is any obstruction anywhere,
I will try to clear it and work it out.

00:43:15.996 --> 00:43:17.200
Now what do you do?

00:43:17.200 --> 00:43:20.000
You don't have to do anything about it,
as I said.

00:43:20.000 --> 00:43:25.600
But these hands, I have to show you,
they represent all of the chakras.

00:43:25.600 --> 00:43:29.280
All your hands, you have to put them
towards Me like this, you see.

00:43:29.280 --> 00:43:32.200
So the vibrations that flow
from my being will flow

00:43:32.200 --> 00:43:33.760
just to your fingers,

00:43:33.760 --> 00:43:38.545
and then you will start to receive
through this centre.

00:43:38.545 --> 00:43:39.600
Then you go to that centre there,

00:43:39.600 --> 00:43:45.425
and they will send a message
of stimulation to the Kundalini

00:43:45.425 --> 00:43:47.600
with pulsation.
And then your Kundalini will rise.

00:43:47.600 --> 00:43:52.080
Now all the names of these chakras
and different things,

00:43:52.080 --> 00:43:57.840
I hope you have brought it for them.
Have you got it?

00:43:57.840 --> 00:43:58.320
They have got it for you there.

00:43:58.320 --> 00:44:00.960
So you can go back home
and see for yourself.

00:44:00.960 --> 00:44:04.400
But first of all, get there.

00:44:04.400 --> 00:44:06.880
And once you get it,
try to stabilize.

00:44:06.880 --> 00:44:11.109
Many people who get it,
they feel very happy, and they just go back.

00:44:11.109 --> 00:44:11.360
No, that's not the way.

00:44:11.360 --> 00:44:15.920
Try to learn and try to understand
what it is. Master it.

00:44:15.920 --> 00:44:21.481
You can cure—we have cured cancer.

00:44:21.481 --> 00:44:22.480
Cancer cannot be cured
by anything else but Sahaja Yoga.

00:44:22.480 --> 00:44:24.880
This is the only solution for cancer.

00:44:24.880 --> 00:44:36.800
But, you see,
it is difficult to convince people.

00:44:36.800 --> 00:45:35.520
What is the reason for cancer?
Let's find out what is the reason.

00:45:35.520 --> 00:45:36.218
And it's a very simple reason:

00:45:36.218 --> 00:45:36.274
it is the over-activity
of the sympathetic nervous system

00:45:36.274 --> 00:45:36.309
which creates imbalances within us.

00:45:36.309 --> 00:45:39.280
And it can be only cured
if you put the parasympathetic there.

00:45:39.280 --> 00:45:43.040
And this parasympathetic is the one
which gives you all the power

00:45:43.040 --> 00:45:46.400
and all the nourishment that is needed

00:45:46.400 --> 00:45:50.240
to fulfil the needs
of the sympathetic system.

00:45:50.240 --> 00:45:54.760
It is like a car
which is travelling very fast

00:45:54.760 --> 00:45:57.840
and the petrol is finished.

00:45:57.840 --> 00:46:06.320
If you put that car to the mains,
and the source is feeding in,

00:46:06.320 --> 00:46:11.440
then there is no necessity
for that car to be exhausted.

00:46:11.440 --> 00:46:13.920
This is the same thing as
putting you to the mains,

00:46:13.920 --> 00:46:18.320
from where the source is,
from where you get the source,

00:46:18.320 --> 00:46:27.600
that you have up to that point,
which is very much limited,

00:46:27.600 --> 00:46:39.570
which you have exhausted
and which has to be refilled.

00:46:39.570 --> 00:46:39.600
And it has to happen that way.

00:46:39.600 --> 00:46:43.600
Because it is so important
that it has to be free.

00:46:43.600 --> 00:46:44.800
All that is important.

00:46:44.800 --> 00:46:50.000
But the feeding has to be
absolutely free. It has to be spontaneous.

00:46:50.000 --> 00:46:52.720
We have taken so many things for granted

00:46:52.720 --> 00:46:57.760
that we do not know that
our Sahaja Yoga also

00:46:57.760 --> 00:47:00.960
can be taken very much for granted
when you achieve it.

00:47:00.960 --> 00:47:04.236
It happens to many other Sahaja Yogis.

00:47:04.236 --> 00:47:08.240
But one has to know that
after getting your Realisation,

00:47:08.240 --> 00:47:10.560
you have to look after yourself.

00:47:10.560 --> 00:47:18.160
And this Realisation is the first time
any evolution has been in a conscious mind.

00:47:18.160 --> 00:47:24.063
So far, all the evolutions that we have had,
let us say, from amoeba to this stage,

00:47:24.063 --> 00:47:24.080
were unconscious.

00:47:24.080 --> 00:47:25.520
But this will be different.

00:47:25.520 --> 00:48:23.440
You will know that you have evolved.
You have become that.

00:48:28.000 --> 00:48:33.120
I am a Mother
and my ways are little motherly.

00:48:33.120 --> 00:48:38.080
And motherly ways are very ancient.

00:48:38.080 --> 00:48:43.040
And she knows how to bring
her children above things.

00:48:43.040 --> 00:48:46.560
And that's why it is called as Maya ways.

00:48:46.560 --> 00:48:50.720
And she brings her children
to the right way.

00:48:50.720 --> 00:48:53.760
And sometimes,
I have to scold some people

00:48:53.760 --> 00:48:57.200
who just don't listen to Me, sometimes.

00:48:57.200 --> 00:49:01.520
But it is not that I make you
surrender your wisdom,

00:49:01.520 --> 00:49:04.720
but your ego gets
automatically surrendered,

00:49:04.720 --> 00:49:07.755
which is keeping you away from your Self.

00:49:07.755 --> 00:49:11.360
Once you get the beauty of your Self,
you become so relaxed

00:49:11.360 --> 00:49:14.960
and so happy with yourself,

00:49:14.960 --> 00:49:20.000
that automatically
you drop off all your so-called vices.

00:49:20.000 --> 00:49:25.031
Because the vices are there
because you are bored, that's why.

00:49:25.031 --> 00:49:25.600
And they just drop.

00:49:25.600 --> 00:49:26.687
I don't have to say,
"Don't do this, and don't do that".

00:49:26.687 --> 00:49:34.080
They just drop off because you start getting
drawn into your own being, your own Self.

00:49:34.080 --> 00:49:36.240
And it's such a beautiful life.

00:49:36.240 --> 00:49:39.920
And then the yoga starts
between your Self,

00:49:39.920 --> 00:49:47.410
and a beautiful relationship,
very pure,

00:49:47.410 --> 00:49:48.240
steps in, not in material,
not emotionally,

00:49:48.240 --> 00:49:52.040
but a feeling of belonging to One,

00:49:52.040 --> 00:49:59.676
of belonging to the whole Being,
you can call it, the Primordial Being.

00:49:59.676 --> 00:50:27.506
The whole is pure,
you start feeling in the ocean of such people.

00:50:27.506 --> 00:50:31.081
May God bless you.

00:50:31.081 --> 00:50:31.106
Put your hands toward Me.

00:50:31.106 --> 00:50:31.161
And another request I have—
please take your shoes off

00:50:31.161 --> 00:50:31.196
because you ground yourself better.

00:50:31.196 --> 00:50:33.040
And there is no shopping going on here.

00:50:36.880 --> 00:50:39.920
You are here to get something.

00:50:39.920 --> 00:50:44.234
You are not here to demand,
but to get something.

00:50:44.234 --> 00:50:45.360
It is your own wealth.

00:50:45.360 --> 00:50:52.201
So we are not shopping here,
we are getting something for our own wealth.

00:50:52.201 --> 00:50:54.720
So we should not be angry about people,
and we should not be angry about it.

00:50:54.720 --> 00:50:59.680
But it is the time.
It's so simple, try to be simple.

00:50:59.680 --> 00:51:01.760
Please put your hands straight forwards.

00:51:01.760 --> 00:51:15.006
Now, the people who are Realized,
as I told you,

00:51:15.006 --> 00:51:16.081
they will later on come to tell you
if there is a problem in your centres.

00:51:16.081 --> 00:51:16.905
I have to also tell you that
you can cure brain diseases,

00:51:16.905 --> 00:51:19.520
and nervous diseases
and also emotional problems.

00:51:19.520 --> 00:51:22.476
Very easy, very easy to do.

00:51:22.476 --> 00:51:24.480
But first of all,
you need to get your Self-realisation.

00:51:24.480 --> 00:51:28.560
Once you get it,
then you will know how to treat it,

00:51:28.560 --> 00:51:30.640
and in the most simple manner.

00:51:30.640 --> 00:51:43.200
It has to be extremely simple.

00:51:43.200 --> 00:51:52.160
Please put your hands like this.

00:51:52.160 --> 00:51:57.040
Some of you may feel
your eyes looking down.

00:51:57.040 --> 00:52:00.240
For such people, I would request
that they close their eyes, it is better.

00:52:00.240 --> 00:52:09.520
Because the eyelids are looking down
because the pupil inside is dilating.

00:52:09.520 --> 00:52:13.840
Just try to close your eyes
in case you feel they are looking down.

00:52:13.840 --> 00:52:22.875
In case your eyes are flickering,
then you have to open your eyes.

00:52:22.875 --> 00:52:26.552
Just stay on your eyelids.

00:52:26.552 --> 00:52:31.680
Best is to close them.
Just close them.

00:52:31.680 --> 00:52:32.800
Just watch your mind.

00:52:32.800 --> 00:52:35.440
Ask the mind to tell you
if there is any thought.

00:52:35.440 --> 00:52:38.069
What are you thinking? Ask the mind.

00:52:38.069 --> 00:52:39.440
That's the best way to do it.

00:52:42.560 --> 00:52:47.117
If you can close your eyes
without flickering, just try.

00:52:47.117 --> 00:52:49.692
If you can close your eyes
without flickering, you are the best.

00:52:49.692 --> 00:52:49.712
That's the best way.

00:52:49.712 --> 00:52:49.750
You can achieve your Self-realisation.

00:52:49.750 --> 00:53:16.480
This will solve most
of your problems automatically.

00:53:31.600 --> 00:53:32.480
Now what are the centres you are catching?

00:53:32.480 --> 00:53:35.040
It's that of Christ.

00:53:35.040 --> 00:53:37.360
For that, I have to tell you
why you are catching.

00:53:37.360 --> 00:53:45.036
Because one thing he has told us to do:
we have to forgive others.

00:53:45.036 --> 00:53:46.000
You have to just say,
"I forgive all of them".

00:53:47.920 --> 00:53:51.040
Not to bear any embitterment in mind.

00:53:51.040 --> 00:53:57.394
Because if you do not forgive, also,
it's just a myth.

00:53:57.394 --> 00:53:57.424
You do not do anything for it.

00:53:57.424 --> 00:55:29.920
On the contrary,
you are playing in&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:55:29.920 --> 00:55:51.930
the hands of people.

00:55:51.930 --> 00:55:51.994
Just close your eyes and say,
"I forgive. I forgive all of them".

00:55:51.994 --> 00:55:53.600
Still you have to say, "I forgive".

00:55:53.600 --> 00:55:54.160
All of us.

00:55:54.160 --> 00:56:20.856
Because I think that's one of the centres
which is catching.

00:56:20.856 --> 00:56:20.880
Please say, "I forgive".

00:56:20.880 --> 00:56:23.280
Another centre on the left-hand side,

00:56:24.240 --> 00:56:26.960
for the people who feel
they are guilty of this.

00:56:26.960 --> 00:56:29.920
This is all a fashion going on.
It is very wrong.

00:56:29.920 --> 00:56:33.600
Because this is the temple of God
and you have no business to condemn it.

00:56:34.480 --> 00:56:37.680
So, those who think
that they are guilty have to say,

00:56:37.680 --> 00:56:39.680
"I'm not guilty". Within yourself.

00:56:39.680 --> 00:56:55.880
At least thrice, please say that,
"I'm not guilty".

00:58:22.960 --> 00:58:24.160
From left to the right.

00:58:24.160 --> 00:58:29.027
Some of you have got an imbalance within,
because some of you are very hard-working people.

00:58:29.027 --> 00:58:32.760
You have got an imbalance within,
from left to the right.

00:58:32.760 --> 00:58:39.095
And now you can all raise
your Kundalini like this,

00:58:39.095 --> 00:58:39.120
and then you tie it high.

00:58:39.120 --> 00:58:53.657
One hand towards Me, the left side.
With the right hand,

00:58:53.657 --> 00:58:53.767
see for yourself.

00:58:53.766 --> 00:58:54.024
Are you feeling cool breeze
in your hand?

00:58:54.024 --> 00:58:55.360
I felt it on my hands
before you mentioned it.

00:58:55.360 --> 00:58:55.840
You did?

00:58:55.840 --> 00:59:01.280
Yes. Yes, actually,
I thought there was some draft in here.

00:59:01.280 --> 00:59:03.440
You are great, I must say.

00:59:03.440 --> 00:59:06.400
Really, you are great,
it happened so easily.

00:59:06.400 --> 00:59:09.040
Yes, that's something which happens
with people like this.

00:59:09.040 --> 00:59:11.253
You too have that?

00:59:11.253 --> 00:59:11.280
Yes, I felt it on my heart.

00:59:11.280 --> 00:59:13.996
Just imagine, so great people are here!

00:59:13.996 --> 00:59:15.680
You see, so great.

00:59:15.680 --> 00:59:17.520
Now let's see,
all of you should feel it.

